msgid ""
"As stated in the xref:data-access/oxm.adoc#oxm-introduction[introduction], a "
"marshaller serializes an object to XML, and an unmarshaller deserializes XML "
"stream to an object. This section describes the two Spring interfaces used "
"for this purpose."
msgstr ""

