#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/oxm.adoc:394
msgid ""
"The `jaxb2-marshaller` element configures a "
"`org.springframework.oxm.jaxb.Jaxb2Marshaller`, as the following example "
"shows:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/oxm.adoc:402
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can provide the list of classes to bind to the marshaller "
"by using the `class-to-be-bound` child element:"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block -
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/oxm.adoc:410
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\t<oxm:jaxb2-marshaller id=\"marshaller\">\n"
"\t\t<oxm:class-to-be-bound "
"name=\"org.springframework.ws.samples.airline.schema.Airport\"/>\n"
"\t\t<oxm:class-to-be-bound "
"name=\"org.springframework.ws.samples.airline.schema.Flight\"/>\n"
"\t\t...\n"
"\t</oxm:jaxb2-marshaller>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/oxm.adoc:413
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/data-access/oxm.adoc:474
msgid "The following table describes the available attributes:"
msgstr ""

